(Overview) Tj
T*
(Thermochemistry studies heat changes during chemical reactions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Learning Objectives) Tj
T*
(- Explain the meaning of Thermochemistry in Chemistry using accurate subject vocabulary.) Tj
T*
(- Describe the key ideas behind exothermic and endothermic processes and energy) Tj
T*
(diagrams.) Tj
T*
(- Apply Thermochemistry to examples such as comparing heat flow in combustion and) Tj
T*
(decomposition.) Tj
T*
