(5. Independent Study Guidance) Tj
T*
(For independent study, the learner should revisit the explanation and then practise with) Tj
T*
(tasks that reflect identifying and interpreting energy changes. The most effective habit) Tj
T*
(is to read the worked example slowly, restate each step in simple words, and then) Tj
T*
(attempt a similar question alone. This turns Thermochemistry into something the student) Tj
T*
(can genuinely study and understand without depending completely on a teacher.) Tj
T*
() Tj
