(Key Ideas To Remember) Tj
T*
(- Thermochemistry should first be understood as a chemical idea before it is treated as) Tj
T*
(an exam topic.) Tj
T*
(- The learner must understand exothermic and endothermic processes and energy diagrams) Tj
T*
(because it controls how questions in Thermochemistry are answered correctly.) Tj
T*
(- A strong answer in Thermochemistry uses the correct chemical reasoning process and) Tj
T*
(explains why that method fits the task.) Tj
T*
(- Comparing heat flow in combustion and decomposition is the type of application that) Tj
T*
(helps move the topic from explanation to mastery.) Tj
T*
() Tj
