(Step-By-Step Method) Tj
T*
(1. Read the question or example and identify the part connected to Thermochemistry.) Tj
T*
(2. Recall the specific rule, process, or principle behind exothermic and endothermic) Tj
T*
(processes and energy diagrams.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct chemical reasoning process step by step instead of jumping to the) Tj
T*
(answer.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the result carefully and confirm that it matches the requirement of the topic.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Worked Examples) Tj
T*
(Worked Example 1) Tj
T*
(1. Start with an example based on comparing heat flow in combustion and decomposition.) Tj
T*
(2. Identify the exact idea in exothermic and endothermic processes and energy diagrams) Tj
T*
(that the question is testing.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct method for Thermochemistry step by step without skipping reasoning.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the final answer and explain why it is correct.) Tj
T*
() Tj
